{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/stand-in-line","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Stani u Red","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U racunarskim naukama, <dfn>queue</dfn> je apstraktna <dfn>struktura podataka</dfn> u kojoj se elementi cuvaju po redosledu. Novi elementi se dodaju na kraj reda, a stariji uklanjaju sa pocetka reda.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244c6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napisite funkciju <code>nextInLine</code> koja prima niz (<code>arr</code>) i broj (<code>item</code>) kao argumente.</p>\n<p>Dodajte broj na kraj niza, zatim uklonite prvi element niza.</p>\n<p>Funkcija <code>nextInLine</code> treba da vrati uklonjeni element.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18307,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/stand-in-line"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function nextInLine(arr, item) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n  \n  return item;\n  // Only change code above this line\n}\n\n// Setup\nlet testArr = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5];\n\n// Display code\nconsole.log(\"Before: \" + JSON.stringify(testArr));\nconsole.log(nextInLine(testArr, 6));\nconsole.log(\"After: \" + JSON.stringify(testArr));","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>nextInLine([], 5)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(nextInLine([], 5));"},{"text":"<p><code>nextInLine([], 1)</code> treba da vrati <code>1</code